<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Situs Diblokir</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71, #3498db);
            font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }
        .container:hover {
            transform: scale(1);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }
        .icon-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .icon img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .icon img:hover {
            transform: rotate(5deg);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #34495e;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #c0392b;
            background-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #2980b9;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            .icon img {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <div class="icon">
                <img src="images/stop.png" alt="Warning Icon">
            </div>
        </div>
        <h1>Situs Diblokir!</h1>
        <p>Karena mengandung konten berikut:</p>
        <p class="highlight">Pornografi, Judi, Phishing/Malware, Sara</p>
        <p>SESUAI UNDANG-UNDANG RI NOMOR 19 TAHUN 2016 PASAL 40 (2A) DAN (2B)<br> TENTANG INFORMASI DAN TRANSAKSI ELEKTRONIK.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Jika tidak bertentangan maka silakan hubungi Kementerian Komunikasi dan Informatika Indonesia.</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:aduankonten@mail.kominfo.go.id">aduankonten@mail.kominfo.go.id</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>